This page is specifically for you - the newcomer who has questions, concerns, and wants to understand how this all works before diving in.

## Why Databayt

Databayt is a collaborative open-source ecosystem designed to accelerate development. With a patterned, searchable code library, developers can start projects up to 70% complete—never from scratch. While open source has come a long way and countless codebases already exist, there's still real value in building a well-structured, indexed library where code follows consistent patterns and architecture. Databayt is about creating that shared standard—together. It's not just practical; it's exciting to shape a clean, reusable codebase as a community—making development faster for everyone, and driving collective progress for Databayt as a publicly traded entity.



